\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"398\" data-end=\"416\">Nama</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"398\" data-end=\"534\"><br data-start=\"416\" data-end=\"419\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Organisasi ini bernama <strong data-start=\"442\" data-end=\"533\">Gerakan Pramuka Penggalang Gugus Depan {{ data_nomor_gudep }} {{ nama_sekolah }}</strong>.</span></p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"398\" data-end=\"534\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"536\" data-end=\"627\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"536\" data-end=\"566\">Pasal 2</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"536\" data-end=\"627\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"536\" data-end=\"566\">Tempat Kedudukan</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"536\" data-end=\"627\"><br data-start=\"566\" data-end=\"569\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Organisasi ini berkedudukan di {{ data_alamat_sekolah }}.</span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"629\" data-end=\"779\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"629\" data-end=\"656\">Pasal 3</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"629\" data-end=\"779\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"629\" data-end=\"656\">Waktu Berdiri</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"629\" data-end=\"779\"><br data-start=\"656\" data-end=\"659\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Gugus Depan ini didirikan pada tanggal {{ data_tanggal_berdiri }} dan berlaku untuk jangka waktu yang tidak ditentukan.</span></p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"629\" data-end=\"779\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"786\" data-end=\"827\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"790\" data-end=\"827\">BAB II </strong></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"786\" data-end=\"827\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"790\" data-end=\"827\">AZAS, TUJUAN, DAN FUNGSI</strong></span></h3>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"961\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"847\">Pasal 4&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"961\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"847\">&nbsp;Azas</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"961\"><br data-start=\"847\" data-end=\"850\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Gerakan Pramuka berazaskan Pancasila dan berlandaskan Undang-Undang Dasar Negara Republik Indonesia Tahun 1945.</span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"963\" data-end=\"1201\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"963\" data-end=\"1201\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"963\" data-end=\"983\">Pasal 5</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"963\" data-end=\"1201\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"963\" data-end=\"983\">Tujuan</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"963\" data-end=\"1201\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Tujuan Gerakan Pramuka adalah membentuk setiap anggota muda agar memiliki kepribadian yang beriman, bertakwa, berakhlak mulia, berjiwa patriotik, taat hukum, disiplin, dan menjunjung tinggi nilai-nilai luhur bangsa.</span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"1203\" data-end=\"1342\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"1203\" data-end=\"1342\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"1203\" data-end=\"1223\">Pasal 6</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"1203\" data-end=\"1342\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"1203\" data-end=\"1223\">Fungsi</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1203\" data-end=\"1342\"><br data-start=\"1223\" data-end=\"1226\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Gerakan Pramuka berfungsi sebagai penyelenggara pendidikan kepanduan nonformal di luar sekolah dan di luar keluarga.</span></p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1203\" data-end=\"1342\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"1349\" data-end=\"1378\">&nbsp;</h3>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"1349\" data-end=\"1378\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"1353\" data-end=\"1378\">BAB III</strong></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"1349\" data-end=\"1378\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"1353\" data-end=\"1378\">KEANGGOTAAN</strong></span></h3>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"1380\" data-end=\"1407\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"1380\" data-end=\"1405\">Pasal 7</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"1380\" data-end=\"1407\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"1380\" data-end=\"1405\">Keanggotaan</strong></span></p>\n<ol data-start=\"1408\" data-end=\"1676\">\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"1408\" data-end=\"1567\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1411\" data-end=\"1567\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Anggota terdiri dari:</span><br data-start=\"1432\" data-end=\"1435\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">a. <strong data-start=\"1441\" data-end=\"1457\">Anggota Muda</strong>: Pramuka Penggalang usia 11&ndash;15 tahun.</span><br data-start=\"1495\" data-end=\"1498\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">b. <strong data-start=\"1504\" data-end=\"1522\">Anggota Dewasa</strong>: Pembina, Pelatih, dan Majelis Pembimbing.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"1568\" data-end=\"1615\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1571\" data-end=\"1615\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Keanggotaan bersifat sukarela dan terbuka.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"1616\" data-end=\"1676\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1619\" data-end=\"1676\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Anggota wajib menaati kode kehormatan dan aturan Pramuka.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"1683\" data-end=\"1710\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"1687\" data-end=\"1710\">BAB IV</strong></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"1683\" data-end=\"1710\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"1687\" data-end=\"1710\">ORGANISASI</strong></span></h3>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"1712\" data-end=\"1747\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"1712\" data-end=\"1745\">Pasal 8</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"1712\" data-end=\"1747\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"1712\" data-end=\"1745\">Struktur Organisasi</strong></span></p>\n<ol data-start=\"1748\" data-end=\"1928\">\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"1748\" data-end=\"1866\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1751\" data-end=\"1866\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Gugus Depan terdiri dari:</span><br data-start=\"1776\" data-end=\"1779\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">a. Majelis Pembimbing Gugus Depan</span><br data-start=\"1815\" data-end=\"1818\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">b. Pembina Pramuka</span><br data-start=\"1839\" data-end=\"1842\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">c. Dewan Penggalang</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"1867\" data-end=\"1928\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1870\" data-end=\"1928\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Tiap Gugus Depan memiliki regu-regu sesuai jumlah anggota.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"1935\" data-end=\"1962\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"1939\" data-end=\"1962\">BAB V</strong></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"1935\" data-end=\"1962\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"1939\" data-end=\"1962\">SUMBER DANA</strong></span></h3>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"1964\" data-end=\"2019\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"1964\" data-end=\"1989\">Pasal 9 </strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"1964\" data-end=\"2019\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"1964\" data-end=\"1989\">Sumber Dana</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1964\" data-end=\"2019\"><br data-start=\"1989\" data-end=\"1992\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Sumber dana berasal dari:</span></p>\n<ol data-start=\"2020\" data-end=\"2170\">\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2020\" data-end=\"2038\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2023\" data-end=\"2038\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Iuran anggota</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2039\" data-end=\"2073\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2042\" data-end=\"2073\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Bantuan dari sekolah/orangtua</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2074\" data-end=\"2108\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2077\" data-end=\"2108\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Sumbangan yang tidak mengikat</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2109\" data-end=\"2170\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2112\" data-end=\"2170\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Usaha mandiri yang tidak bertentangan dengan nilai Pramuka</span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"2177\" data-end=\"2205\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2180\" data-end=\"2205\">ANGGARAN RUMAH TANGGA</strong></span></h2>\n<hr class=\"\" data-start=\"2207\" data-end=\"2210\">\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"2212\" data-end=\"2239\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2216\" data-end=\"2239\">BAB I </strong></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"2212\" data-end=\"2239\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2216\" data-end=\"2239\">KEANGGOTAAN</strong></span></h3>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"2241\" data-end=\"2275\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2241\" data-end=\"2273\">Pasal 1</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"2241\" data-end=\"2275\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2241\" data-end=\"2273\">Syarat Keanggotaan</strong></span></p>\n<ol data-start=\"2276\" data-end=\"2462\">\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2276\" data-end=\"2354\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2279\" data-end=\"2354\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Berstatus sebagai siswa {{ nama_sekolah }} dan berusia 11&ndash;15 tahun.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2355\" data-end=\"2408\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2358\" data-end=\"2408\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Mengisi formulir pendaftaran dan membayar iuran.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2409\" data-end=\"2462\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2412\" data-end=\"2462\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Siap mengikuti kegiatan rutin dan latihan Pramuka.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"2464\" data-end=\"2491\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2464\" data-end=\"2489\">Pasal 2</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"2464\" data-end=\"2491\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2464\" data-end=\"2489\">Hak Anggota</strong></span></p>\n<ol data-start=\"2492\" data-end=\"2648\">\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2492\" data-end=\"2530\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2495\" data-end=\"2530\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Mengikuti semua kegiatan Pramuka.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2531\" data-end=\"2569\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2534\" data-end=\"2569\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Mendapat pembinaan dan pelatihan.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2570\" data-end=\"2607\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2573\" data-end=\"2607\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Menyampaikan pendapat dan saran.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2608\" data-end=\"2648\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2611\" data-end=\"2648\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Mendapat penghargaan sesuai prestasi.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"2650\" data-end=\"2683\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2650\" data-end=\"2681\">Pasal 3</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"2650\" data-end=\"2683\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2650\" data-end=\"2681\">Kewajiban Anggota</strong></span></p>\n<ol data-start=\"2684\" data-end=\"2839\">\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2684\" data-end=\"2723\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2687\" data-end=\"2723\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Menjaga nama baik Gerakan Pramuka.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2724\" data-end=\"2772\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2727\" data-end=\"2772\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Mengikuti seluruh kegiatan dengan disiplin.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2773\" data-end=\"2814\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2776\" data-end=\"2814\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Menjunjung Dasa Dharma dan Trisatya.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2815\" data-end=\"2839\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2818\" data-end=\"2839\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Membayar iuran rutin.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"2846\" data-end=\"2879\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2850\" data-end=\"2879\">BAB II</strong></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"2846\" data-end=\"2879\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2850\" data-end=\"2879\">DEWAN PENGGALANG</strong></span></h3>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"2881\" data-end=\"2925\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2881\" data-end=\"2923\">Pasal 4</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"2881\" data-end=\"2925\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2881\" data-end=\"2923\">Pembentukan Dewan Penggalang</strong></span></p>\n<ol data-start=\"2926\" data-end=\"3063\">\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2926\" data-end=\"3001\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2929\" data-end=\"3001\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Terdiri dari perwakilan regu (ketua regu, wakil, dan sekretaris regu).</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"3002\" data-end=\"3033\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3005\" data-end=\"3033\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Dipilih secara demokratis.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"3034\" data-end=\"3063\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3037\" data-end=\"3063\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Masa bakti 1 tahun ajaran.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"3065\" data-end=\"3103\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"3065\" data-end=\"3101\">Pasal 5</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"3065\" data-end=\"3103\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"3065\" data-end=\"3101\">Tugas Dewan Penggalang</strong></span></p>\n<ol data-start=\"3104\" data-end=\"3238\">\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"3104\" data-end=\"3153\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3107\" data-end=\"3153\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Merencanakan dan melaksanakan program kerja.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"3154\" data-end=\"3205\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3157\" data-end=\"3205\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Menjadi penghubung antara anggota dan pembina.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"3206\" data-end=\"3238\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3209\" data-end=\"3238\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Membina kerja sama antaregu.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"3245\" data-end=\"3293\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"3249\" data-end=\"3293\">BAB III</strong></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"3245\" data-end=\"3293\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"3249\" data-end=\"3293\">PEMBINA DAN MAJELIS PEMBIMBING</strong></span></h3>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"3295\" data-end=\"3330\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"3295\" data-end=\"3328\">Pasal 6</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"3295\" data-end=\"3330\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"3295\" data-end=\"3328\">Pembina Gugus Depan</strong></span></p>\n<ol data-start=\"3331\" data-end=\"3499\">\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"3331\" data-end=\"3394\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3334\" data-end=\"3394\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Ditunjuk oleh sekolah dan memiliki kompetensi kepramukaan.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"3395\" data-end=\"3461\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3398\" data-end=\"3461\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Bertugas membina dan mendampingi kegiatan pramuka penggalang.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"3462\" data-end=\"3499\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3465\" data-end=\"3499\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Menjadi penanggung jawab kegiatan.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"3501\" data-end=\"3557\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"3501\" data-end=\"3555\">Pasal 7 </strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"3501\" data-end=\"3557\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"3501\" data-end=\"3555\">Majelis Pembimbing Gugus Depan (Mabigus)</strong></span></p>\n<ol data-start=\"3558\" data-end=\"3708\">\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"3558\" data-end=\"3592\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3561\" data-end=\"3592\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Dipimpin oleh Kepala Sekolah.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"3593\" data-end=\"3665\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3596\" data-end=\"3665\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Bertugas memberikan arahan umum dan dukungan moral maupun material.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"3666\" data-end=\"3708\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3669\" data-end=\"3708\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Mengawasi pelaksanaan kegiatan Pramuka.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"3715\" data-end=\"3752\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"3719\" data-end=\"3752\">BAB IV</strong></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"3715\" data-end=\"3752\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"3719\" data-end=\"3752\">PROGRAM DAN KEGIATAN</strong></span></h3>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"3754\" data-end=\"3784\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"3754\" data-end=\"3782\">Pasal 8</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"3754\" data-end=\"3784\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"3754\" data-end=\"3782\">Jenis Kegiatan</strong></span></p>\n<ol data-start=\"3785\" data-end=\"3952\">\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"3785\" data-end=\"3813\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3788\" data-end=\"3813\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Latihan rutin mingguan.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"3814\" data-end=\"3875\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3817\" data-end=\"3875\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Kegiatan tahunan: Persami, lomba, pelantikan, pelatihan.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"3876\" data-end=\"3952\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3879\" data-end=\"3952\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Kegiatan insidental: kerja bakti, kampanye sosial, peringatan hari besar.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"3954\" data-end=\"3990\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"3954\" data-end=\"3988\">Pasal 9</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"3954\" data-end=\"3990\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"3954\" data-end=\"3988\">Evaluasi dan Laporan</strong></span></p>\n<ol data-start=\"3991\" data-end=\"4076\">\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"3991\" data-end=\"4032\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"3994\" data-end=\"4032\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Kegiatan dievaluasi setiap semester.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"4033\" data-end=\"4076\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"4036\" data-end=\"4076\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Laporan kegiatan disampaikan ke Mabigus.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"4083\" data-end=\"4108\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"4087\" data-end=\"4108\">BAB V</strong></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"4083\" data-end=\"4108\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"4087\" data-end=\"4108\">LAIN-LAIN</strong></span></h3>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"4110\" data-end=\"4230\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"4110\" data-end=\"4141\">Pasal 10</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"4110\" data-end=\"4230\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"4110\" data-end=\"4141\">Perubahan AD/ART</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"4110\" data-end=\"4230\"><br data-start=\"4141\" data-end=\"4144\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Perubahan dilakukan melalui musyawarah anggota dengan persetujuan Pembina dan Mabigus.</span></p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"4110\" data-end=\"4230\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"4232\" data-end=\"4365\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"4232\" data-end=\"4254\">Pasal 11</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\" data-start=\"4232\" data-end=\"4365\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"4232\" data-end=\"4254\">Penutup</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"4232\" data-end=\"4365\"><br data-start=\"4254\" data-end=\"4257\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">AD/ART ini berlaku sejak ditetapkan dan dapat ditinjau ulang secara berkala sesuai perkembangan Gugus Depan.</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><br></h1>\n\n                ','2025-07-31 17:00:00','2025-07-31 17:56:00'),(78,'Anggaran Dasar Dan Anggaran Rumah Tangga (AD/ART) Komite Sekolah',NULL,'ADART','\n                <h2>Anggaran Dasar & Anggaran Rumah Tangga</h2>\n                    <h3>Komite Sekolah [Nama Sekolah]</h3>\n\n                    <div class=\"section\">\n                        <h3>Anggaran Dasar</h3>\n                        <h4>Bab I: Nama dan Kedudukan</h4>\n                        <ol>\n                            <li>Organisasi ini bernama <strong>Komite Sekolah [Nama Sekolah]</strong>.</li>\n                            <li>Kedudukan Komite Sekolah berada di lingkungan [Nama Sekolah], yang beralamat di [Alamat Sekolah].</li>\n                        </ol>\n\n                        <h4>Bab II: Asas, Tujuan, dan Fungsi</h4>\n                        <ol>\n                            <li><strong>Asas:</strong> Komite Sekolah berasaskan musyawarah dan gotong royong dalam mendukung pendidikan.</li>\n                            <li><strong>Tujuan:</strong>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <li>Meningkatkan mutu pendidikan melalui partisipasi masyarakat.</li>\n                                    <li>Mendukung penyelenggaraan pendidikan yang lebih transparan dan akuntabel.</li>\n                                </ul>\n                            </li>\n                            <li><strong>Fungsi:</strong>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <li>Memberikan pertimbangan dalam kebijakan pendidikan di sekolah.</li>\n                                    <li>Membantu perencanaan dan pengawasan program sekolah.</li>\n                                    <li>Menggalang dukungan masyarakat untuk kemajuan sekolah.</li>\n                                </ul>\n                            </li>\n                        </ol>\n\n                        <h4>Bab III: Keanggotaan</h4>\n                        <ol>\n                            <li>Anggota Komite Sekolah terdiri dari orang tua siswa, tokoh masyarakat, alumni, dan pemerhati pendidikan.</li>\n                            <li>Keanggotaan bersifat sukarela dan tidak mengikat.</li>\n                        </ol>\n\n                        <h4>Bab IV: Kepengurusan</h4>\n                        <ol>\n                            <li>Struktur kepengurusan Komite Sekolah terdiri dari:\n                                <ul>\n                                    <li>Ketua</li>\n                                    <li>Wakil Ketua</li>\n                                    <li>Sekretaris</li>\n                                    <li>Bendahara</li>\n                                    <li>Anggota</li>\n                                </ul>\n                            </li>\n                            <li>Masa bakti kepengurusan ditetapkan untuk [X] tahun dan dapat diperpanjang berdasarkan musyawarah.</li>\n                        </ol>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"section\">\n                        <h3>Anggaran Rumah Tangga</h3>\n                        <h4>Bab I: Keanggotaan</h4>\n                        <ol>\n                            <li>Anggota Komite Sekolah wajib mengikuti aturan yang ditetapkan dalam AD/ART.</li>\n                            <li>Setiap anggota memiliki hak suara dalam pengambilan keputusan.</li>\n                        </ol>\n\n                        <h4>Bab II: Tugas dan Wewenang</h4>\n                        <ol>\n                            <li><strong>Ketua:</strong> Bertanggung jawab atas kepemimpinan organisasi dan koordinasi program.</li>\n                            <li><strong>Wakil Ketua:</strong> Membantu Ketua dalam menjalankan tugasnya.</li>\n                            <li><strong>Sekretaris:</strong> Mengelola administrasi dan dokumentasi Komite Sekolah.</li>\n                            <li><strong>Bendahara:</strong> Mengelola keuangan dan laporan keuangan Komite Sekolah.</li>\n                            <li><strong>Anggota:</strong> Mendukung dan menjalankan tugas sesuai dengan bidang masing-masing.</li>\n                        </ol>\n\n                        <h4>Bab III: Rapat dan Pengambilan Keputusan</h4>\n                        <ol>\n                            <li>Rapat Komite Sekolah diadakan secara berkala atau sesuai kebutuhan.</li>\n                            <li>Keputusan diambil berdasarkan musyawarah mufakat atau pemungutan suara.</li>\n                        </ol>\n\n                        <h4>Bab IV: Keuangan</h4>\n                        <ol>\n                            <li>Keuangan Komite Sekolah bersumber dari sumbangan sukarela, bantuan pemerintah, dan partisipasi masyarakat.</li>\n                            <li>Penggunaan dana harus sesuai dengan kebutuhan sekolah dan dilaporkan secara transparan.</li>\n                        </ol>\n\n                        <h4>Bab V: Perubahan AD/ART</h4>\n                        <ol>\n                            <li>Perubahan AD/ART dapat dilakukan melalui rapat anggota dengan persetujuan mayoritas.</li>\n                            <li>Perubahan harus didokumentasikan dan disetujui oleh seluruh pengurus.</li>\n                        </ol>\n\n                        <h4>Bab VI: Pembubaran</h4>\n                        <ol>\n                            <li>Komite Sekolah dapat dibubarkan berdasarkan kesepakatan bersama dan sesuai dengan peraturan yang berlaku.</li>\n                        </ol>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"footer\">\n                        <p style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Ditetapkan di:</strong> [Nama Kota/Kabupaten]</p>\n                        <p style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Pada Tanggal:</strong> [Tanggal Penetapan]</p>\n                        <p style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Kepala Sekolah</strong></p>\n                        <br><br><br>\n                        <p style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>[Nama Kepala Sekolah]</strong></p>\n                    </div>\n                ','2025-07-31 17:00:00','2025-07-31 17:56:00'),(79,'Pengantar Kegiatan Study Banding',NULL,'Pengantar','\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Kepada Yth.</strong><br>{{ data_instansi_tujuan }}<br>di Tempat</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dengan hormat,</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bersama surat ini kami sampaikan bahwa siswa dan guru dari <strong>{{ nama_sekolah }}</strong> akan melaksanakan kegiatan study banding ke instansi Bapak/Ibu pada tanggal <strong>{{ data_tanggal }}</strong>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tujuan dari kegiatan ini adalah untuk belajar dan bertukar pengalaman mengenai praktik pendidikan yang telah diterapkan di instansi Bapak/Ibu, serta untuk memperdalam pemahaman kami terkait berbagai metode dan inovasi yang digunakan dalam meningkatkan kualitas pendidikan.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dalam kegiatan study banding ini, kami berharap dapat memperoleh wawasan baru yang berguna untuk diterapkan di sekolah kami, serta menjalin hubungan yang lebih baik antara instansi kami dengan Bapak/Ibu, guna meningkatkan kualitas pendidikan secara bersama-sama.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Demikian surat pengantar ini kami sampaikan. Atas penerimaan dan sambutannya, kami ucapkan terima kasih yang sebesar-besarnya. Kami berharap kegiatan ini dapat berjalan dengan lancar dan memberikan manfaat yang besar bagi kedua belah pihak.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n','2025-07-31 17:00:00','2025-07-31 17:56:00'),(80,'Pengantar Kegiatan Magang',NULL,'Pengantar','\n\n            <table style=\"width: 85.042%; border-collapse: collapse; border-width: 0px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 13.0856%; border-width: 0px;\"><strong>No. Surat:</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 86.8451%; border-width: 0px;\">{{ data_no_surat }}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 13.0856%; border-width: 0px;\"><strong>Lampiran:</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 86.8451%; border-width: 0px;\">{{ data_lampiran }}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 13.0856%; border-width: 0px;\"><strong>Perihal:</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 86.8451%; border-width: 0px;\">Pengantar Kegiatan Magang</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Kepada Yth.</strong><br>Pimpinan {{ data_nama_instansi }}<br>di Tempat</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Dengan hormat,</p>\n<p>Dengan ini kami sampaikan bahwa siswa berikut dari <strong>{{ nama_sekolah }}</strong> akan melaksanakan kegiatan magang/praktik