: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Telp: [Nomor Kontak]</span></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">DAN</span></h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong>[NAMA LEMBAGA/INSTANSI 2]</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Alamat: [Alamat Lengkap]</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Telp: [Nomor Kontak]</span></p>\n<h3 class=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-start=\"152\" data-end=\"177\">&nbsp;</h3>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1256\" data-end=\"1281\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"1260\" data-end=\"1281\">I. LATAR BELAKANG</strong></span></h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1283\" data-end=\"1659\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Koperasi sekolah merupakan salah satu unit usaha di lingkungan sekolah yang bertujuan mendukung kebutuhan siswa dan guru, khususnya dalam penyediaan perlengkapan pendidikan seperti alat tulis. Untuk menjamin ketersediaan barang yang berkualitas dan terjangkau, maka diperlukan kerja sama yang saling menguntungkan antara koperasi sekolah dengan penyedia alat tulis terpercaya.</span></p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1283\" data-end=\"1659\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1666\" data-end=\"1695\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"1670\" data-end=\"1695\">II. MAKSUD DAN TUJUAN</strong></span></h3>\n<ol data-start=\"1697\" data-end=\"2080\">\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"1697\" data-end=\"1804\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1700\" data-end=\"1804\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Menyediakan alat tulis dan perlengkapan sekolah yang lengkap dan berkualitas untuk kebutuhan koperasi.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"1805\" data-end=\"1890\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1808\" data-end=\"1890\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Menjamin kontinuitas suplai alat tulis sesuai kebutuhan dan permintaan koperasi.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"1891\" data-end=\"1984\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1894\" data-end=\"1984\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Menjalin hubungan kerja sama jangka panjang yang saling menguntungkan kedua belah pihak.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"1985\" data-end=\"2080\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1988\" data-end=\"2080\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Mendukung kelancaran kegiatan belajar mengajar melalui ketersediaan alat tulis yang memadai.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2087\" data-end=\"2124\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2091\" data-end=\"2124\">III. RUANG LINGKUP KERJA SAMA</strong></span></h3>\n<ol data-start=\"2126\" data-end=\"2559\">\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2126\" data-end=\"2241\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2129\" data-end=\"2241\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Penyediaan barang-barang berupa alat tulis, buku tulis, perlengkapan kantor, dan kebutuhan pendidikan lainnya.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2242\" data-end=\"2336\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2245\" data-end=\"2336\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Penentuan jenis dan jumlah barang berdasarkan kebutuhan yang diajukan oleh PIHAK PERTAMA.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2337\" data-end=\"2397\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2340\" data-end=\"2397\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Penetapan harga barang berdasarkan kesepakatan bersama.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2398\" data-end=\"2451\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2401\" data-end=\"2451\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Pengiriman barang tepat waktu sesuai permintaan.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2452\" data-end=\"2559\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2455\" data-end=\"2559\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Pemberian diskon khusus koperasi sekolah dan pelayanan pengembalian barang yang rusak atau tidak sesuai.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12pt;font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2566\" data-end=\"2595\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2570\" data-end=\"2595\">IV. HAK DAN KEWAJIBAN</strong></span></h3>\n<h4 class=\"\" data-start=\"2597\" data-end=\"2620\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2602\" data-end=\"2620\">PIHAK PERTAMA:</strong></span></h4>\n<ul data-start=\"2621\" data-end=\"2991\">\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2621\" data-end=\"2739\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2623\" data-end=\"2739\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Menyampaikan daftar kebutuhan dan jumlah alat tulis secara tertulis atau melalui media komunikasi yang disepakati.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2740\" data-end=\"2826\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2742\" data-end=\"2826\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Melakukan pembayaran sesuai kesepakatan waktu dan mekanisme yang telah ditentukan.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2827\" data-end=\"2912\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2829\" data-end=\"2912\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Menjaga hubungan baik serta memberikan masukan atas kualitas layanan PIHAK KEDUA.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\" data-start=\"2913\" data-end=\"2991\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2915\" data-end=\"2991\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\">Menyediakan tempat dan sarana pendukung untuk penyaluran barang ke koperasi.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 class=\"\" data-start=\"2993\" data-end=\"3014\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \"times new roman\", times, serif;\"><strong data-start=\"2998\" data-end=\"3014\">PIHAK KEDUA:</strong></span></h4>\n<ul data-start=\"3015\" data-end=\"3333\">\n<li class=\"\" 